===Etymology===
From {{compound|en|slime|ball}}; sense 1 (“a [[round#Adjective|round]] [[lump#Noun|lump]] made up of or [[coat#Verb|coated]] with [[slime#Noun|slime]] or a [[slimelike|slime-like]] [[substance]]”) is a {{calque|en|de|Schleimkugel|nocap=1}}, from {{m|de|Schleim||mucus; slime}} + {{m|de|Kugel||ball}}, while sense 1.1 may be a {{calque|en|de|Schleimball|nocap=1}} (from {{m|de|Schleim}} + {{m|de|Ball||ball}}).<ref>{{R:OED Online|pos=n|id=75830622|date=December 2018}}</ref>

